OL,3,CMSP 'overwhelmed' to become MBE
OL,5,FAn MSP has told how she felt
OL,6,F"overwhelmed" when she learned she
OL,7,Fwill become a Member of the Order of
OL,8,Fthe British Empire (MBE).
OL,10,FPam Duncan-Glancy is recognised in the
OL,11,FKing's Birthday Honours for years of
OL,12,Fpublic and political service.
OL,14,FSpeaking to the PA news agency, the
OL,15,FLabour Glasgow MSP ` the first
OL,16,Fpermanent wheelchair user to be
OL,17,Felected to the Scottish Parliament and
OL,18,Fa tireless disability campaigner `
OL,19,Fsaid she had learned about the honour
OL,20,Fin a text from her husband after she
OL,21,Fhad received an email about it.
