OL,3,CMSP 'overwhelmed' to become MBE
OL,5,F"I was overwhelmed, to be honest, and
OL,6,Fcould hardly believe what I was
OL,7,Freading," she said.
OL,9,F"I'm really, really proud to have been
OL,10,Fgiven this honour for the work that
OL,11,FI've done in the community and for
OL,12,Fdisability rights.
OL,14,F"It's a real honour to do this.
OL,16,F"When I got elected as an MSP, I said
OL,17,FI was a wee working class woman in a
OL,18,Fwheelchair. To think that I could be a
OL,19,Fwee working class woman in a
OL,20,Fwheelchair who's also got an MBE, I
OL,21,Fjust thought that was pretty special."
