OL,3,CMSP 'overwhelmed' to become MBE
OL,5,FWhile receiving such an honour from
OL,6,Fthe Palace requires discretion, Ms
OL,7,FDuncan-Glancy admitted she struggled
OL,8,Fkeeping it all a secret.
OL,10,F"I told my sister, obviously my
OL,11,Fhusband knows and I told my team and a
OL,12,Fcouple of friends, but it was really
OL,13,Fdifficult to keep it quiet," she said.
OL,15,FWith just 11 months until the next
OL,16,FHolyrood election, the MSP said there
OL,17,Fis "loads more" the Scottish
OL,18,FParliament and politics more widely
OL,19,Fhas to do for more disabled people to
OL,20,Fseek election.
