OL,3,CMSP 'overwhelmed' to become MBE
OL,5,F"We need to support people to be
OL,6,Factive in their communities in the
OL,7,Ffirst place," she said.
OL,9,F"For disabled people, it can often be
OL,10,Fabout giving them help to get out of
OL,11,Fbed in the morning.
OL,13,F"There's quite a mountain to climb for
OL,14,Fus to support disabled people to get
OL,15,Finto politics and it's a mountain we
OL,16,Fabsolutely have to climb, because
OL,17,Fthere should be no space about us,
OL,18,Fwithout us.
