OL,3,CMSP 'overwhelmed' to become MBE
OL,5,F"We need to do everything we possibly
OL,6,Fcan to get more representation of
OL,7,Fdisabled people, not just in
OL,8,FParliament or councils, but
OL,9,Feverywhere."
OL,11,FElected in 2021, Ms Duncan-Glancy has
OL,12,Fimpressed in her first term as an MSP,
OL,13,Fbeing given a spot on the Scottish
OL,14,FLabour frontbench before even making
OL,15,Fit to Holyrood, when she was appointed
OL,16,Fsocial security spokeswoman by leader
OL,17,FAnas Sarwar in the early weeks of his
OL,18,Ftenure.
